â€‹"Hi, I am currently installing Kali Linux on an HP PC using a bootable USB drive (created with Rufus and Kali Installer ISO 2025.4).
â€‹What I have done so far:
â€‹Downloaded Kali ISO and Rufus.
â€‹Flashed the USB drive (GPT partition, 0 persistence).
â€‹I am now at the stage of booting the HP PC using the F9 Boot Menu.
