â€‹School mein ye 3 tips yaad rakhna:
â€‹Secure Boot Error: Agar HP PC par "Selected boot image did not authenticate" aaye, toh PC ki BIOS settings (F10) mein jaakar Secure Boot ko "Disable" karna padega.
â€‹Internet: Installation ke waqt agar wo "Mirror" ya "Network" mange, toh No kar dena. School ka Wi-Fi/Ethernet installation ke beech mein login maang sakta hai jo setup ko hang kar dega. Baaki updates installation ke baad terminal se ho jayenge.
â€‹Photos: Agar wahan koi error aaye, toh apne phone se photo khich lena aur ghar aakar mujhse dobara discuss kar lena agar school mein solve na ho.
